---
title: Quick Salt-Pepper Chicken & Asian Mushroom Rice with Garlic Aioli & Coriander
description: Has a rice ever looked this delicious because it’s making our dreams come true. The veggies and mushrooms in the rice are zested with lemon juice and soy sauce for a deep medley of flavours. The chicken is spiced and peppered to perfection so the combination of everything is the stuff of dreams.
